{"tid":777791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《Monster Hunter World 》遭下架 騰訊股價挫逾2%","createTime":"2018-08-13T07:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T14:16:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf65e8aa880e84514fec839f4c35dbbc8b50e58","tid":777791,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"騰訊（700）周三公布業績，股價今早低見361.6元，最新跌2.32%至361.4元，暫成交36.1億元。<br />\n<br />\n負責中國發行的騰訊WeGame平台，今日宣布 《魔物獵人 世界》即時下架，因為部分遊戲內容不符當地政策法規，遭到大量舉報，已被取消營運資格，消息拖累騰訊股價表現。<br />\n<br />\n近年騰訊對PC市場發展停滯不前，《魔物獵人 世界》被視為公司打入該市場的強心針，而另一PC平台Steam潛在中國玩家達2,000萬。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，由於WeGame及Steam均有代理《魔物獵人 世界》，故WeGame急著要在Steam版本發售前先行上市，導致未完全通過法令審核。據了解，Steam 版《魔物獵人 世界》標準版售價：308元人民幣，貴WeGame9元。而Steam版不支援簡體中文，而WeGame則標榜支援簡體，並指「會進行符合中國人的知優化」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180813/58556263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58556263&d=%2FjI2VTkhbvnYLJGZcMNtS4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=2106c6db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58556263&h=466e74e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180813/58556263</a>"},{"pid":"543e55be45bf42593c58812b52863501aa6d962e","tid":777791,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"下個係收steam 皮"},{"pid":"2b6c2e5141a8b481b906192c5059e71d113df638","tid":777791,"uid":112583,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:56:51.000Z","msg":"背脊向天用黎食架屌<br />\n斬完又唔食緊係BAN你"},{"pid":"bfa80a2b43281e2fb6f82647164f6382a165407e","tid":777791,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T07:58:00.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"36bb8f46498f9d7577a5ad5cec34d2ce11a340c3","tid":777791,"uid":98289,"like":9,"